transcripts: The Hudson area rug by Kenneth Cole reaction home was designed exclusively for Bed Bath and Beyond. The undulating lines of this rug create soft motion, deep blue tones are reminiscent of running river water. This rug is available in four sizes including accent, area, and runners sizes and is easy care polypropylene. The Hudson area rug is part of the Kenneth Cole reaction home collection. It is available exclusively online and at select a Bed Bath and Beyond stores.
